@startuml
!include ../style.puml

node "RocksDB Physical Keys" {
  map "Key 'Account1'" as k1 {
    "Account1\\x00<InvTs:110>" => "$200"
    "Account1\\x00<InvTs:90>" => "$150"
    "Account1\\x00<InvTs:50>" => "$100"
  }
}

note right of k1
  **Encoding Structure:**
  1. **Logical Key:** "Account1"
  2. **Separator:** 0x00 byte
  3. **Inverted Timestamp:** (Max_Long - WallClock)
  
  *Because RocksDB sorts lexicographically, 
  inverted timestamps ensure the newest 
  version appears first!*
end note
@enduml
